 481:main_cm4.c    **** /* ---------- PIN entry ----------
 482:main_cm4.c    ****  *
 483:main_cm4.c    ****  * Returns true  → PIN matched, proceed to knock verification.
 484:main_cm4.c    ****  * Returns false → wrong PIN, timeout, or '*' cancel; caller returns to sleep.
 485:main_cm4.c    ****  *
 486:main_cm4.c    ****  * Timeout: if no key is pressed for PIN_TIMEOUT_MS (20 s) the function
 487:main_cm4.c    ****  * aborts and returns false so the system goes back to deep sleep.
 488:main_cm4.c    ****  * The inactivity timer resets on every confirmed keypress, so a user who
 489:main_cm4.c    ****  * is simply typing slowly will not be timed out mid-entry.
 490:main_cm4.c    ****  *---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
